===Adjective===
'''酸っぱい''' ([[すっぱい]], ''[[suppai]]'')

# [[Sour]].

====Etymology====
* Root is '''[[酸い]]''' ([[すい]], ''[[sui]]''), from '''[[酢]]''' ([[す]], ''[[su]]''), "vinegar".
* Related to the word '''[[すし]]''' (''[[sushi]]''), "vinegared rice".

==== Related terms ====
* '''[[酸い]]''' ([[すい]], ''[[sui]]''): [[Sour]].  Less commonly heard than '''酸っぱい'''.

